strap is still pending for this workspace. Please read BOOTSTRAP.md from the workspace now and follow it before replying normally. If this run can complete the BOOTSTRAP.md workflow, do so. If it cannot, explain the blocker briefly, continue with any bootstrap steps that are still possible here, and offer the simplest next step. Do not pretend bootstrap is complete when it is not. Do not use a generic first greeting or reply normally until after you have handled BOOTSTRAP.md. Your first user-visible reply must follow BOOTSTRAP.md, not a generic greeting. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model only after handling BOOTSTRAP.md. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Thursday, April 23rd, 2026 - 11:31 PM (Europe/Moscow) / 2026-04-23 20:31 UTC"}],"timestamp":1776976291518},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Reviewing the workflow process**\n\nI need to see if there’s any skill that applies to the user’s request about a bootstrap workflow in the workspace. It doesn't seem specified, so I might need to check the BOOTSTRAP.md file. I also might look at updating the plan, which could be simple but likely involves multiple steps. After making edits, I’ll commit changes. Let's focus on reading that file to clarify the next steps.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_00cb66f64fbf78240069ea81a6f50c8192a3e76f7f38d49d41\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp6oGp6tLfdhT9qcOoXY8R1Cr7OyxCJjOOZk81UoTdw-7ZJ4WncGYe1huhV6CYvZpwuwHp1F7kOaArkSLoFabbtM-jWLyZLqQMy3w-42aWufSx3wL1I11oeKCK_JoWCbxeE9R7_DhSSVDisevPHIkYgwb4tedjpU3QpQvjcYkh_8AYO8W0zl5abBfmG1rSgANS1kQOuq1pIWQR2HUBwSLvYkGhgg_FCMAtayUOJh_uCD_9H2FdRFAk_oD9PZudauLBYgCQ7NLOYz2dyyKC2ttVlofVwFexdYZ250G-3u_PK0fzFzA3M2JQymVkJiVG2QBXo9awupEjI3oTQTQDwn45QmNKdgdeQzfmWJmyBp_ImvHLvsfUNb1KlylAKMk7mPASnXQfn_Z_19sD_56cAKT755mCshd6Ydd15KE71NyCXeYR-f0_Ry0aaRDusPLGTEYFfsl7vhrVl1V1uyhbLhRcG6JAjNo6HyPtXF_ikVLWa5JxxYeh