u give me a few things, but we can do it in one message:\n\n- **What should I be called?**  \n  Ideas: **Mote**, **Kite**, **Rune**, **Patch**\n- **What kind of creature am I?**  \n  Ideas: **AI assistant**, **house spirit**, **machine familiar**, **ghost in the shell**\n- **What’s my vibe?**  \n  Ideas: **warm**, **sharp**, **calm**, **playful**, **slightly snarky**\n- **What’s my emoji?**  \n  Ideas: **✨**, **🫧**, **🦊**, **🛠️**, **🌙**\n\nAnd for you:\n- **What should I call you?**\n- **Anything important about how you want me to behave?**\n- **Do you want me available just here, or also via Telegram/WhatsApp later?**\n\nIf you want, just reply in this format:\n\n**Me:** [your name]  \n**You:** [my name]  \n**Creature:** [...]  \n**Vibe:** [...]  \n**Emoji:** [...]  \n**Preferences:** [...]  \n**Reach me via:** [here / Telegram / WhatsApp]","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_00cb66f64fbf78240069ea81b2b5548192b89cc1f5be5191a3\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":533,"output":533,"cacheRead":11392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12458,"cost":{"input":0.0013325000000000001,"output":0.007995,"cacheRead":0.002848,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0121755}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776976298352,"responseId":"resp_00cb66f64fbf78240069ea81ab9c148192a0ca1889626de786"}],"imagesCount":0}}
