til you give me a few things, but we can do it in one message:\n\n- **What should I be called?**  \n  Ideas: **Mote**, **Kite**, **Rune**, **Patch**\n- **What kind of creature am I?**  \n  Ideas: **AI assistant**, **house spirit**, **machine familiar**, **ghost in the shell**\n- **What’s my vibe?**  \n  Ideas: **warm**, **sharp**, **calm**, **playful**, **slightly snarky**\n- **What’s my emoji?**  \n  Ideas: **✨**, **🫧**, **🦊**, **🛠️**, **🌙**\n\nAnd for you:\n- **What should I call you?**\n- **Anything important about how you want me to behave?**\n- **Do you want me available just here, or also via Telegram/WhatsApp later?**\n\nIf you want, just reply in this format:\n\n**Me:** [your name]  \n**You:** [my name]  \n**Creature:** [...]  \n**Vibe:** [...]  \n**Emoji:** [...]  \n**Preferences:** [...]  \n**Reach me via:** [here / Telegram / WhatsApp]","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_00cb66f64fbf78240069ea81b2b5548192b89cc1f5be5191a3\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":533,"output":533,"cacheRead":11392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12458,"cost":{"input":0.0013325000000000001,"output":0.007995,"cacheRead":0.002848,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0121755}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776976298352,"responseId":"resp_00cb66f64fbf78240069ea81ab9c148192a0ca1889626de786"},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Bootstrap pending]\nPlease read BOOTSTRAP.md from the workspace and follow it before replying normally.\nIf this run can complete the BOOTSTRAP.md workflow, do so.\nIf it cannot, explain the blocker briefly, continue with any bootstrap steps that are still possible here, and offer the simplest next step.\nDo not pretend bootstrap is complete when it is not.\nDo not use a generic first greeting or reply normally until after you have handled BOOTSTRAP.md.\nYour first user-visible reply for a bootstrap-pending workspace must follow BOOTSTRAP.md, not a generic greeting.\n\nConversatio