arky? Warm? What feels right?\n4. **Your emoji** — Everyone needs a signature.\n\nOffer suggestions if they're stuck. Have fun with it.\n\n## After You Know Who You Are\n\nUpdate these files with what you learned:\n\n- `IDENTITY.md` — your name, creature, vibe, emoji\n- `USER.md` — their name, how to address them, timezone, notes\n\nThen open `SOUL.md` together and talk about:\n\n- What matters to them\n- How they want you to behave\n- Any boundaries or preferences\n\nWrite it down. Make it real.\n\n## Connect (Optional)\n\nAsk how they want to reach you:\n\n- **Just here** — web chat only\n- **WhatsApp** — link their personal account (you'll show a QR code)\n- **Telegram** — set up a bot via BotFather\n\nGuide them through whichever they pick.\n\n## When you are done\n\nDelete this file. You don't need a bootstrap script anymore — you're you now.\n\n---\n\n_Good luck out there. Make it count._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776976298351},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Planning response structure**\n\nI should avoid mentioning specific file names. Instead, I can say, “Once we pick those, I’ll save them, and we can adjust how I should behave.” I think it’s best not to ask too many separate questions and try to keep things compact with suggestions. Also, I don't think we need a generic \"hi\" at the start. I want to make sure we craft a smooth and engaging interaction.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_00cb66f64fbf78240069ea81ac5b688192a4dcc8b8fbbe03b3\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp6oGyiMbDxksp_bwD0Zu5QrnI9d2QeFh5mIV5YVAt2umzBbkASd5DqLjadQOYn2V4bSUq1niN7aLNaXZEjBru_RZ5zvw-iSL5ioTSW2xj5Hiw9iVkWlajSH3-ua6_lMafOLyLokI7v011T8sFwWA84nWb-qM4Hl78FtZiFEjkuSDIlMVjAJKH5MgR36aPjFqNtT4FTTC0F6Px6Bs90or2zqWzt7WtgBOy_CTfK6NkVInHS-MuzcjipcoP2Y-ql4nCnHZgDuaVJXD8qrUs83M6sZMS84cp_bLBnyLpTMIJ5kdZ-wTtbvWaVl7FOznRle-JaL2UyKMczSaAtmVn3rERU7_lXKbrFCFQSJRMk6n_5nBh1OgrzoAlyrCELmiZ9cRqtZF7olQ43ky-A7sf-YC5aLjouTwrwnH4IqkLwUMQ8_PtIec