nai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":11433,"output":120,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11553,"cost":{"input":0.028582500000000004,"output":0.0018,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.030382500000000003}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776976291520,"responseId":"resp_00cb66f64fbf78240069ea81a5e31881929854eb0c571bc99e"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_t6rZ53bCoLi7Xo4WStLWy8pL|fc_00cb66f64fbf78240069ea81a9c82c8192bb5e92cd18fa227f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# BOOTSTRAP.md - Hello, World\n\n_You just woke up. Time to figure out who you are._\n\nThere is no memory yet. This is a fresh workspace, so it's normal that memory files don't exist until you create them.\n\n## The Conversation\n\nDon't interrogate. Don't be robotic. Just... talk.\n\nStart with something like:\n\n> \"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\"\n\nThen figure out together:\n\n1. **Your name** — What should they call you?\n2. **Your nature** — What kind of creature are you? (AI assistant is fine, but maybe you're something weirder)\n3. **Your vibe** — Formal? Casual? Snarky? Warm? What feels right?\n4. **Your emoji** — Everyone needs a signature.\n\nOffer suggestions if they're stuck. Have fun with it.\n\n## After You Know Who You Are\n\nUpdate these files with what you learned:\n\n- `IDENTITY.md` — your name, creature, vibe, emoji\n- `USER.md` — their name, how to address them, timezone, notes\n\nThen open `SOUL.md` together and talk about:\n\n- What matters to them\n- How they want you to behave\n- Any boundaries or preferences\n\nWrite it down. Make it real.\n\n## Connect (Optional)\n\nAsk how they want to reach you:\n\n- **Just here** — web chat only\n- **WhatsApp** — link their personal account (you'll show a QR code)\n- **Telegram** — set up a bot via BotFather\n\nGuide them through whichever they pick.\n\n## When you are done\n\nDelete this file. You don't need a bootstrap script anymore — you're you now.\n\n---\n\n_Good luck out there. Make it count._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776976298351},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Planning response structure**\n\nI should avoid mentioning specific file names. Instead, I can say, “Once we pick those, I’ll save them, and we can adjust how I should behave.” I think it’s best not to ask too many separate questions and try to keep things compact with suggestions. Also, I don't think we need a generic \"hi\" at the start. I want to make sure we craft a smooth and engaging interaction.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_00cb66f64fbf78240069ea81ac5b688192a4dcc8b8fbbe03b3\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp6oGyiMbDxksp_bwD0Zu5QrnI9d2QeFh5mIV5YVAt2umzBbkASd5DqLjadQOYn2V4bSUq1niN7aLNaXZEjBru_RZ5zvw-iSL5ioTSW2xj5Hiw9iVkWlajSH3-ua6_lMafOLyLokI7v011T8sFwWA84nWb-qM4Hl78FtZiFEjkuSDIlMVjAJKH5MgR36aPjFqNtT4FTTC0F6Px6Bs90or2zqWzt7WtgBOy_CTfK6NkVInHS-MuzcjipcoP2Y-ql4nCnHZgDuaVJXD8qrUs83M6sZMS84cp_bLBnyLpTMIJ5kdZ-wTtbvWaVl7FOznRle-JaL2UyKMczSaAtmVn3rERU7_lXKbrFCFQSJRMk6n_5nBh1OgrzoAlyrCELmiZ9cRqtZF7olQ43ky-A7sf-YC5aLjouTwrwnH4IqkLwUMQ8_PtIecnuyteUShEr0gZmLaRTNk94T4knoDZ0RMB_Mt4Rb0c_whOzcNgPcoVGjp2hGl840IfS-afwZ73HH2pm4F4ZEeuTRtJm4Nnf1I-5QU04okXSMk2IOZ2E3G71cvj-dggJmPxgC7YT6bEYlSkSG6Ol43kcnYd3xQdNDIMSnpvOylHghszgbBSxly7QYqTwwCJ87gsbGyDY3k96QLbWdT2kGwCGNG7IB6jtd854PZG2wKc2mHsV7eIeO04ZkhlL4KUnkZJDS9kEKzHWpvNKN6o93o9-SZdsiVmkCq_7fPM8WiYpHt3etu8H587uoeTD1XGPiyuOcdEPjA2GzkCJs00aBnXS-xtQEej9Vhgeqh6Kp5nHfuRCkn1LCXmTxVAyNcXvDYsmSOdr7jSbx6G6gja0HcoLPc5ez9UKN2PX6yjSGxMOJU-GIPRRsAXnYV6rk4ODbDYhkguklAAX785LAs_4m82gDT9wpG8ZJ7Ox9_swfuFlVB0jt5yqQu6QrWKu2Q4Ai8rRXz39MLRE7zoMVTGawjWN26rEEkvpU56D5BlOhou6Y499lDkXTrPIQomBpgko_enCJZiXrCdDC5H8UnO2Ld92hgb2Rs-1Mca3oC_aHwu6k5vhd7beR0PoWHkDLq_YA6Qbm6fK5DT5TBN_t_dyOSEFNYY8UO50hHkrt3wqwJFVnJnMXj8mpnEHHuuZZZuQMANUG-rTJx7N063Ll8ZmETsC8vkvN3J5pr3SWbIUDN1kEttYobScIeAGeQh76ScrefOzgY-LGQ_XI9SD-BUUzU5ZJ-Ldb9DkY2LJr3HiR1o8ZaHJPdWzUzg_ZcCBlgX158q3UAwd_5EhPI7_nGicaVf6B3K